snippet.title: Shaktikanta Das Addresses Media, Says No Charge on Debit Card Usage

localized.description:
Economic Affairs Secretary Shaktikanta Das addresses media over demonetisation of Rs 500 and 1000 notes. Shaktikanta says that there will be no charge on debit card usage.
